Description: Fragment of papyrus with 7 lines of Demotic text, in black and red ink on recto, concerning animal omina. Same ms as EA 76624; P. Wien D 6218 and several unnumbered Berlin papyri, also Oxford and Brooklyn.
Curator's comments: To be published by Joachim Friedrich Quack (Heidelberg)
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380687) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380687)
